							<div class="post_wrapper author">
								<div id="about_the_author">
									<div class="gravatar"><a href="https://lithub.com/author/jitkacejkova/"><img src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jitka-Cejkova-100x100.jpeg" width="100" height="100" alt="Jitka Čejková" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></a></div>
									<div class="description author withsidebar">
										<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/jitkacejkova/">Jitka Čejková</a></h6>
										Jitka Čejková is Associate Professor in the Chemical Robotics Laboratory at the University of Chemistry and Technology Prague. Her research focuses on how chemical engineers can contribute to artificial life research.																			</div>
